Package: libnorn
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Mainline DHT, secure sessions and cluster KV library (runtime)
 libnorn is a C library for peer-to-peer applications: a Mainline DHT client
 (BEP-5/BEP-44), authenticated pubkey-addressed sessions and reliable streams
 with NAT traversal, and a class-aware Raft cluster key-value store.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: libnorn-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 libnorn (= ${binary:Version}),
 libsodium-dev,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: Mainline DHT, secure sessions and cluster KV library (development)
 libnorn is a C library for peer-to-peer applications: a Mainline DHT client
 (BEP-5/BEP-44), authenticated pubkey-addressed sessions and reliable streams
 with NAT traversal, and a class-aware Raft cluster key-value store.
 .
 This package contains the headers, the static library, the pkg-config file
 and the libnorn(3) manual page needed to build against libnorn.

Package: norn
Section: net
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: norn command-line client and node daemon
 The norn CLI drives the Mainline DHT directly and acts as a thin IPC client
 to nornd, the node daemon that runs a norn node and hosts the replicated
 cluster key-value store and the fleet SSH/GPG key directory.
 .
 This package contains the norn, nornd and norn-forward programs, their manual
 pages and the systemd units.

Package: libnorn-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Mainline DHT, secure sessions and cluster KV library (documentation)
 libnorn is a C library for peer-to-peer applications: a Mainline DHT client
 (BEP-5/BEP-44), authenticated pubkey-addressed sessions and reliable streams
 with NAT traversal, and a class-aware Raft cluster key-value store.
 .
 This package contains the Doxygen-generated API reference and the design
 documents.
